{"tid":2383052,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★外媒：iOS 14.4 災情總整理","createTime":"2021-01-27T15:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T06:19:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a848c54f435b37c13b1300d1970ef991eab466d","tid":2383052,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T15:54:13.000Z","msg":"目前已經收到百多位網友回報 iOS 14.4 災情，發生錯誤情況如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>iOS錯誤</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n5g上網經常延遲/短暫不能上網<br />\n綠螢幕依然未改善<br />\n解鎖touch id 會卡頓一下 然後又好了<br />\n全黑畫面綠屏和閃屏無解決<br />\n少數用戶發生在解鎖畫面要打開時home不見沒辦法解鎖<br />\niOS 14 用iTunes更新都會卡住，只能參考瘋先生之前提供的方法，下載檔案到電腦再跑一次才可以<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>App 錯誤</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nApp閃退（或會出現閃退情況）：蘋果日報、Instagram、MB3、YouTube、Message<br />\nLine對方聽不懂、語音備忘錄沒有任何聲音、手機開擴音對方聽不到<br />\nMessager打字還是會出現注音文<br />\nLine、ig訊息不會通知<br />\nLine 訊息鈴聲會突然很大聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/ios-14-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fios-14-4&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cUwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=169c7d43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mrmad.com.tw/ios-14-4</a>"},{"pid":"9ce9ce9392977f354a898c21031bbb7b5de46670","tid":2383052,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T15:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80488d21a55b1ba8c44ba7675e4e642528ff59cc","tid":2383052,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T15:56:13.000Z","msg":"我升左！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\